<event name="BEACON_EATER_START" unique="true">
	<preventQuest/>
	<text>It appears the distress call is coming from a civilian station. One of the few brave souls left trying to defend their weak claim to this territory, it seems they've now fallen victim to some sort of attack. Fearful help will never arrive, they're willing to pay you to sort out the issue. They just give one warning - these Lanius aren't like the usual.</text>
