<event name="BEACON_EATER_START_WIN">
	<text>"Thank you so much, you saved us from what could have been a slow and painful death from isolation. I don't know what we were thinking building a station here... Hopefully the beacon will remain functional until a repair team can arrive, but for now let us pay you for your assistance."</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ask if they know what the 'Beacon Eater' is.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Oh... I know a little. From what I understand, he goes by many names. I've heard he feeds exclusively on beacons, which is where his current name comes from. The King of the Lanius Swarm is extremely ancient and vindictive. His swarm is the one that has claimed this territory, and they've been terrorizing the settlers here ever since the Civil War. I'm not sure what you could possibly hope to do, but if you could try and stop the attacks, I'm sure the Union as a whole would be grateful."</text>
			<quest event="QUEST_BEACON_EATER"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Thank them and carry on.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Stay behind and take some time to salvage the 'gift'.</text>
